<section xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
    <title>HTMLInputHidden</title>
    <para>
        This is a <literal>HtmlInputText</literal> component which is not visible to the user.
        It is commonly used as an alternative to cookies to transmit a process id across different
        pages enabling the framework to tie up subsequent HTTP requests into a single process.
    </para>
